summary: An ordinance relating to the vacation of the alley in Block 39, an addition to the Town of Seattle, as laid out on the claims of C. D. Boren and A. A. Denny and H. L. Yesler (commonly known as C. D. Boren's Addition), being the alley in the block bounded by 5th Avenue, Yesler Way. and Terrace Street, and authorizing the Superintendent of Buildings to sign a petition therefor.
